OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWarm but occasionally rather
OL,6,Fcloudy. Driest in southern and eastern
OL,7,Fparts, with the best brighter spells,
OL,8,Fwhile northwestern parts probably
OL,9,Fretaining thicker cloud, and seeing
OL,10,Fsome intermittent light rain and
OL,11,Fdrizzle. Light winds generally
OL,12,Fthroughout.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FMainly fine during the
OL,15,Fevening, but becoming rather cloudy
OL,16,Ffrom the west, with a little rain
OL,17,Fspreading eastwards. Staying warm,
OL,18,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
