OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRather cloudy with a little
OL,6,Frain possible during the morning
OL,7,Fespecially, but tending to become
OL,8,Fdrier into the afternoon, with some
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells developing.
OL,10,FWarm, with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FMostly fine with some sunshine.
OL,14,FTurning very warm and humid towards
OL,15,Fthe weekend, staying mainly dry, but
OL,16,Fwith a small chance of thunderstorms
OL,17,Fon Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
